dct_title_s: Genkon kaisei Ōsaka shigai meisai zenzu zen; Hōryū Jōjun cho.
dct_description_sm: Mounted cover title. Title on map: Ōsaka shigai meisai zenzu. Copperplate print. In Japanese. 2 sheets joined. Relief shown by hachures. Includes 5 insets, distance chart, address chart, timetable of trains, and legend. 1 map: col.; 46 x 70 cm, folded in cover 16 x 10 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
